ation)\">Peer Gynt</a></i> (1998, with Stephan Muller; from Ibsen)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Tibet_Through_the_Red_Box_(play)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tibet Through the Red Box (play)\">Tibet Through the Red Box</a></i> (2004, from Sis)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Yellow_Face_(play)\" title=\"Yellow Face (play)\">Yellow Face</a></i> (2007)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Chinglish_(play)\" title=\"Chinglish (play)\">Chinglish</a></i> (2011)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Short plays</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Dance_and_the_Railroad\" title=\"The Dance and the Railroad\">The Dance and the Railroad</a></i> (1981)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_House_of_Sleeping_Beauties\" title=\"The House of Sleeping Beauties\">The House of Sleeping Beauties</a></i> (1983, from Kawabata)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Sound_of_a_Voice\" title=\"The Sound of a Voice\">The Sound of a Voice</a></i> (1983)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/As_the_Crow_Flies_(play)\" title=\"As the Crow Flies (play)\">As the Crow Flies</a></i> (1986)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Bondage_(play)\" title=\"Bondage (play)\">Bondage</a></i> (1992)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Trying_to_Find_Chinatown\" title=\"Trying to Find Chinatown\">Trying to Find Chinatown</a></i> (1996)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Bang_Kok\" title=\"Bang Kok\">Bang Kok</a></i> (1996)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Merchandising_(play)\" title=\"Merchandising (play)\">Merchandising</a></i> (1999)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Jade_Flowerpots_and_Bound_Feet\" title=\"Jade Flowerpots and Bound Feet\">Jade Flowerpots and Bound Feet</a></i> (2001)</li>\n<li><i><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">The Great Helmsman</a></i> (2007)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/A_Very_DNA_Reunion\" title=\"A Very DNA Reunion\">A Very DNA Reunion</a></i> (2010)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Film/television</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Blind_Alleys\" title=\"Blind Alleys\">Blind Alleys</a></i> (1985, with Kimball)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/M._Butterfly_(film)\" title=\"M. Butterfly (film)\">M. Butterfly</a></i> (1993)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Golden_Gate_(film)\" title=\"Golden Gate (film)\">Golden Gate</a></i> (1994)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Monkey_King_(TV_miniseries)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Monkey King (TV miniseries)\">The Lost Empire</a></i> (2001)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Possession_(2002_film)\" title=\"Possession (2002 film)\">Possession</a></i> (2002, with Jones and LaBute, from Byatt)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Music theatre</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/1000_Airplanes_on_the_Roof\" title=\"1000 Airplanes on the Roof\">1000 Airplanes on the Roof</a></i> (1988, with Glass and Sirlin)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Voyage_(opera)\" title=\"The Voyage (opera)\">The Voyage</a></i> (1992, with Glass)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Silver_River\" title=\"The Silver River\">The Silver River</a></i> (1997, with Sheng)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Aida_(musical)\" title=\"Aida (musical)\">Aida</a></i> (2000, with Woolverton &amp; Falls, John and Rice, from Verdi)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Flower_Drum_Song\" title=\"Flower Drum Song\">Flower Drum Song</a></i> (2001, with Rodgers and Hammerstein, from Fields, Hammerstein, and Lee)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Ainadamar\" title=\"Ainadamar\">Ainadamar</a></i> (2003, with Golijov)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Sound_of_a_Voice_(opera)\" title=\"The Sound of a Voice (opera)\">The Sound of a Voice</a></i> (2003, with Glass)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Tarzan_(musical)\" title=\"Tarzan (musical)\">Tarzan</a></i> (2006, with Collins, from Burroughs)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Alice_in_Wonderland_(opera)\" title=\"Alice in Wonderland (opera)\">Alice in Wonderland</a></i> (2007, with Chin, from Carroll)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Fly_(opera)\" title=\"The Fly (opera)\">The Fly</a></i> (2008, with Shore)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Comedy_and_tragedy_masks.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/26/Comedy_and_tragedy_masks.jpg/29px-Comedy_and_tragedy_masks.jpg\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/26/Comedy_and_tragedy_masks.jpg/44px-Comedy_and_tragedy_masks.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/26/Comedy_and_tragedy_masks.jpg/59px-Comedy_and_tragedy_masks.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"200\" data-file-height=\"204\" /></a></td><td><i>This article on a 2000s play is a <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Stub\" title=\"Wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help Wikipedia by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=The_Great_Helmsman_(play)&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a>.</i><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 15px; display: none;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:2000s-play-stub\" title=\"Template:2000s-play-stub\"><abbr title=\"View this template\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:2000s-play-stub\" title=\"Template talk:2000s-play-stub\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\">t</abbr></a></li><li 